==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hammer-less
<hw>Ham"mer-less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Firearms)</fld> <def>Without
a visible hammer; -- said of a gun having a cock or striker concealed
from sight, and out of the way of an accidental touch.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hammer lock</ent>⟦br⟧
